&lt;p&gt;The Huntress team is seeking a driven and motivated Account Executive. The Account Executive position is a high-volume sales role selling the Huntress cybersecurity Platform to Managed Service Providers. This role is focused on acquiring net new logos while being able to cross-sell and upsell into those accounts for a period of 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will work closely with the Sales Engineering team engaged in full-cycle partner recruitment, handling intro calls to close, and successful onboarding.&lt;/p&gt;
