&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Account Managers to identify accounts with low license deployment and proactively reach out to offer training and resources, and specific deployment plays to drive broader adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct post action check-ins with partners following security incidents to ensure they have the support they need and understand how to prevent future issues, while translating these stories into proof of value for their end clients.&lt;/li&gt;
